-- main loop
-- once per logical tick
-- (0) update ball pos
-- (1) send reset signal to VGA_MOTOR
-- as often as posible
-- (2) collsion with padle
-- (3) resolve collisions with blocks

-- -----------------------------
-- (0)
-- Update ball 1
UPD ball regitser 1

-- Update ball 2
UPD ball register 2
-- ----------------------------
-- (1)
reset the flag somehow.

-- ----------------------------
-- (3)
-- Ball 1 collision if it exists and is not allready dealt with.
-- If dealt with continue otherwise reflect the ball and call block
-- destructor (4).
bra coll 1 
-- hoppa annars till bra coll 2
reflect 1
set coll flag 1
jmp (4) tile destructor

-- Ball 2 collision if it exists and is not allready dealt with.
-- If dealt with continue otherwise reflect the ball and call block
-- destructor (4).
bra coll 2
reflect 1
set coll flag 2
jmp (4) tile destructor


-- ----------------------------------------------------------------
-- (4) Tile destructor
ADD adress register + 1000
STORE &adress registrer, 0
jmp "start of loop" (2)
